# AccessDrivePY

# Connecting Api

1. console.cloud.google.com
2. sign up with the same id with drive
3. click create new project
4. project name
5. click create
6. select project
7. Api & Services
8. dashboard
9. Click Enable Api and services
10. Search Drive API and select
11. Click Enable
12. Click on +Create Cradential
13. Credential Type 
  * google drive api 
  * User Data
14. OAuth concent screen
  * App Name - Anything
  * User support email - Email ID
  * Developer contact Info - Email ID
15. Scopes
  * Save & Continue
16. OAuth Client ID
  * Application ID - Select anything for which you want to create that application.
  * Name It
  * Create Now
17 Download Cradential
  * Download It.
  * Rename It - client_secters.json

# Libraries For Google Auth:
1. Installed pydrive (pip install pydrive)
2. Imported GoogleAuth , GoogleDrive

# Library For File Select Window
1. tkinter
2. Imported filedialog

